{"thig3.2:0.1":"Therigatha 3.2 ","thig3.2:0.2":"Tikanipata ","thig3.2:0.3":"Uttamatherigatha ","thig3.2:1.1":"“Catukkhattum pancakkhattum, ","thig3.2:1.2":"vihara upanikkhamim; ","thig3.2:1.3":"Aladdha cetaso santim, ","thig3.2:1.4":"citte avasavattini. ","thig3.2:2.1":"Sa bhikkhunim upagacchim, ","thig3.2:2.2":"ya me saddhayika ahu; ","thig3.2:2.3":"Sa me dhammamadesesi, ","thig3.2:2.4":"khandhayatanadhatuyo. ","thig3.2:3.1":"Tassa dhammam sunitvana, ","thig3.2:3.2":"Yatha mam anusasi sa; ","thig3.2:3.3":"Sattaham ekapallankena, ","thig3.2:3.4":"Nisidim pitisukhasamappita; ","thig3.2:3.5":"Atthamiya pade pasaresim, ","thig3.2:3.6":"Tamokhandham padaliya”ti. ","thig3.2:4.1":"… Uttama theri …. "}